  <entry>
    <title>关于switch和if else</title>
    <link href="http://顾绿绿のblog.com/2021/10/21/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8Eswitch%E5%92%8Cif-else/"/>
    <id>http://顾绿绿のblog.com/2021/10/21/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8Eswitch%E5%92%8Cif-else/</id>
    <published>2021-10-21T15:12:52.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-11-12T14:20:38.301Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="关于if-else"><a href="#关于if-else" class="headerlink" title="关于if else"></a>关于if else</h1><p>关于if型：当满足这个条件时,执行某个操作,而不满足该条件时,什么都不做.在这种情况下就可以使用这种结构</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">if(某个条件)</span><br><span class="line">语句;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>关于if else型：当满足这个条件时,执行某个操作,当不满足这个条件时,执行另一个操作(和if型区别是如果不满足条件一个是执行另一个操作,而一个是什么都不做)</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">if(某个条件)</span><br><span class="line">语句1;</span><br><span class="line">else</span><br><span class="line">语句2;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="关于if-else-1"><a href="#关于if-else-1" class="headerlink" title="关于if else"></a>关于if else</h1><p>if else型：这种形式的if语句,最终只有一个出口.即当满足条件1时,执行语句1.当不满足条件1时,往下走,判断是否满足条件2,如果还是不满足,则继续往下走,一直走到else语句,说明之前的条件都不满足,最终执行语句4;<br>这个和之前两个的区别是:它存在了多种情况的分析,而之前两个仅仅只有一种情况的分析。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">if(条件1)</span><br><span class="line">语句1;</span><br><span class="line">else if(条件2)</span><br><span class="line">语句2;</span><br><span class="line">else if(条件3)</span><br><span class="line">语句3;</span><br><span class="line">.</span><br><span class="line">else</span><br><span class="line">语句4;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意：if else if else 与if 嵌套的区别:<br>if套if,是当外面条件不满足时,里面的if不会执行<br>而if else if else,是当第一个条件不满足时,判断第二个条件<br>这段解释来自于<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_42805389/article/details/102518733">CSDN博主「浮笙若有梦」的原创文章</a><br>因为书本上的解释过少，我选择copyCSDN博主的文章，较容易理解。</p><h1 id="关于switch"><a href="#关于switch" class="headerlink" title="关于switch"></a>关于switch</h1> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">switch (表达式) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">case 1:</span><br><span class="line">语句体1;break;</span><br><span class="line">case 2:</span><br><span class="line">语句体2;break;</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">                default:</span><br><span class="line">                                语句体n+1;break;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>首先计算出表达式的值。其次，和case依次比较，一旦有对应的值，就会执行相应的语句，在执行的过程中，遇到break就会结束。最后，如果所有的case都和表达式的值不匹配，就会执行default语句体部分，然后程序结束掉。</p><h1 id="今天的编程作业"><a href="#今天的编程作业" class="headerlink" title="今天的编程作业"></a>今天的编程作业</h1><ul><li>编写程序，计算并输出下列分段函数的函数值：<br>y={x<em>x+2</em>x-6 x&lt;0,x!=-3<br>  {x*x-5*x+6 0&lt;=x&lt;10,x!=2,x!=3<br>  {x*x-x-15 x=-3,x=-2,x=3,x&gt;=10<br>答案：<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  int main ()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;      </span><br><span class="line">      int x,y;</span><br><span class="line">      printf (&quot;请输入一个x:&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">      scanf(&quot;%d&quot;,&amp;x) ;</span><br><span class="line">      if(x&lt;0&amp;&amp;x!=-3)</span><br><span class="line">            printf(&quot;%d\n&quot;,y=x*x+2*x-6);</span><br><span class="line">      eles if(0&lt;=x&amp;&amp;x&lt;10&amp;&amp;x!=2&amp;&amp;x!=3)</span><br><span class="line">            printf(&quot;%d\n&quot;,y=x*x-5*x+6);</span><br><span class="line">      eles if(x==-3||x==2||x==3||x&gt;=10)</span><br><span class="line">            printf(&quot;%d\n&quot;,y=x*x-x-15);</span><br><span class="line">      return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>编写程序，从键盘输入年和月，计算并输出该年的该月份共有多少天。</li><li><ul><li>这是我同学的做法：<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include &lt; stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class="line">int main()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;    int year,m;</span><br><span class="line">     scanf(&quot;%d %d&quot;,&amp;year,&amp;m);</span><br><span class="line">     if(((year%100==0&amp;&amp;year%400==0)||(year%4==0&amp;&amp;year%100!=0))&amp;&amp;m==2)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">     printf(&quot;29\n&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;else&#123;</span><br><span class="line">          switch (m) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">          case 1:printf(&quot;31\n&quot;);break;</span><br><span class="line">          case 2:printf(&quot;28\n&quot;);break;</span><br><span class="line">          case 3:printf(&quot;31\n&quot;);break;</span><br><span class="line">          case 4:printf(&quot;30\n&quot;);break;</span><br><span class="line">          case 5:printf(&quot;31\n&quot;);break;</span><br><span class="line">          case 6:printf(&quot;30\n&quot;);break;</span><br><span class="line">          case 7:printf(&quot;31\n&quot;);break;</span><br><span class="line">          case 8:printf(&quot;31\n&quot;);break;</span><br><span class="line">          case 9:printf(&quot;30\n&quot;);break;</span><br><span class="line">          case 10:printf(&quot;31\n&quot;);break;</span><br><span class="line">          case 11:printf(&quot;30\n&quot;);break;</span><br><span class="line">          default:printf(&quot;31\n&quot;);break;</span><br><span class="line">         &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">eturn 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><ul><li>这是我的做法：<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class="line">int main()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">int year,month,day;</span><br><span class="line">printf(&quot;请分别输入年和月: &quot;);</span><br><span class="line">scanf(&quot;%d %d&quot;,&amp;year,&amp;month);</span><br><span class="line">    if(month==2&amp;&amp;((year%100==0&amp;&amp;year%400==0)||(year%4==0&amp;&amp;year%100!=0)))</span><br><span class="line">    printf(&quot;该年该月有29天&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">    else&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    if(month==1||month==3||month==5||month==7||month==8||month==10||month==12)</span><br><span class="line">    printf(&quot;该年该月有31天&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">    else&#123;</span><br><span class="line">               if(month==4||month==6||month==9||month==11)</span><br><span class="line">printf(&quot;该年该月有30天&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">               else</span><br><span class="line">             printf(&quot;该年该月有28天&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">                       &#125;</span><br><span class="line">           &#125;</span><br><span class="line">return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li></ul><h1 id="作业的思考"><a href="#作业的思考" class="headerlink" title="作业的思考"></a>作业的思考</h1><p>以上，我认为这一题使用if else较为方便，且我们的作业还要写在纸张上交给老师，我就可以偷懒少些一点嘿嘿。我看了大家的作业基本都是使用switch，较少使用if else。这个程序研究了一个小时有余，虽然关于运行上是没有问题，但是还是担心有bug。<br>希望以后学得更多之后返回来检查可以完美化这个程序。<br>这是今天学习的if else和switch语句的具体内容以及大神的解释和我个人的理解。PS：就算是我的方法去做这个题目，但是我还是感觉到十分的麻烦。<br>希望以后可以提到提升简化这个程序。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;关于if-else&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#关于if-else&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;关于if else&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;关于if else&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;关于if型：当满足这个条件时,执行某个操作,而不满足该条件时,什么都不做.在这种情况</summary>
      
    
    
    
